Package: testOTM
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate Ranks and Quantiles using Optimal Transportation
Version: 0.03
Date: 2019-06-28
Authors@R: person(given = "Peng", family = "Xu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "px2132@columbia.edu")
Author: Peng Xu <px2132@columbia.edu> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Peng Xu <px2132@columbia.edu>
Description: This package implements the multivariate ranks and quantiles, together with their application in statistical testing, that based on the semi-discrete optimal transportation. The underlying geometric computation is performed by the Geogram library.
